        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Apply PCA to determine the optimal number of principal components to retain based on explained variance. Visualize the explained variance ratio to aid in this determination.\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Instructions\n",
        "1. Import `PCA` from `sklearn.decomposition`.\n",
        "2. Instantiate `PCA` without specifying `n_components` to retain all components initially.\n",
        "3. Fit PCA to the `df_normalized` data.\n",
        "4. Calculate the cumulative explained variance ratio.\n",
        "5. Plot the explained variance ratio (individual and cumulative) against the number of components to find the 'elbow' point, which suggests the optimal number of components."
