      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "The next logical step, following the introduction of the PCA subtask, is to implement the PCA process. This involves importing the necessary library, applying PCA to the normalized data, calculating the explained variance, and then visualizing it as per the subtask's instructions.\n",
        "\n"
